criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Without any treatment before imaging examination;

          2. MR of the hip joint was performed within three months before the operation and the
             image quality was good;

          3. Arthroscopic operation was performed in our hospital, and the operation records were
             complete.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. History of hip surgery, tumor, or previous fracture;

          2. Unclear image, serious artifact, or incomplete clinical data.
